body:
He has done just about everything Faker has, is the only other player to attend 3 world championships, let alone win them, plus he went 3-0 just these semis against Peanut, the &quot;best jungler in the world.&quot; He has a long legacy of being a top tier jungler, but while everyone is always,&quot; OMG FAKER LAST HIT A MINION. HE IS SUCH A GOD!!!!!&quot; the general opinion of bengi is  &quot;yeah, he is pretty good on the whole, but let&#039;s talk some more about Faker again.&quot;

Don&#039;t get me wrong, I am not trying to take anything away from Faker. It is just that I think Bengi deserves a little more credit than he gets often from casters and fans. This dude has been around a long time, has plenty of trophies under his belt, and makes a strong case for the best jungler to play League of Legends.

I might be alone here, but I just thought I would throw that out there.
